### Technology Stack (Current Versions)

- **Next.js 15.5.2** - App Router architecture with React Server Components
- **React 19.1.0** - Latest stable with concurrent features
- **TypeScript 5.5.4** - Strict mode enabled for type safety
- **Tailwind CSS v4** - Utility-first styling with theme-aware utilities
- **Framer Motion 11.3.28** - Production animations and interactions
- **React Hook Form 7.52.2 + Zod 4.0.0** - Form handling with schema validation

### Theme System Architecture

- **Default Theme**: Dark (DM Sans font family with modern, tech-focused aesthetics)
- **Light Theme**: Inter font family with modern, clean, professional styling
- **CSS Custom Properties**: Runtime theme switching without component changes
- **Semantic Design Tokens**: Theme-aware color tokens (background-primary, text-primary, etc.)
- **HSL Color Format**: Better color manipulation and accessibility

### Key Features Implemented

- ✅ **Design system** with glass morphism and gradients
- ✅ **Responsive animations** using Framer Motion
- ✅ **Theme management** with dark/light mode persistence and font switching
- ✅ **Form validation** using React Hook Form + Zod schemas
- ✅ **SEO optimization** with metadata and structured markup
- ✅ **Accessibility compliance** with WCAG AA standards
- ✅ **Performance optimization** with Next.js Image and code splitting
- ✅ **Developer experience** with ESLint, Prettier, and TypeScript
